<hymn_number>424</hymn_number>
<title>zhǔ wǒ xiàng nǐ jǔ shǒu 迦南424</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ xiàng nǐ jǔ shǒu, wǒ de xīn kě wàng nǐ, xiàng jiǔ hàn zhī de qiè qiè pàn yǔ.
 zhǔ wǒ de xīn gàn kě, qiú nǐ chōng mǎn wǒ, shǐ wǒ dé zhe huó shuǐ de jiāng hé.
 zhǔ wǒ de líng yōu shāng, nǐ lái yī zhì wǒ, ràng wǒ měi tiān dōu wèi nǐ ér huó.
 zhǔ wǒ de shēn pí bèi, nǐ lái fú chí wǒ, hé nǐ yī qǐ gāng qiáng zhàn shèng zuì è.</lyrics>
</song>